  "context": "A carrier's special-investigations unit picks which of 80 model-flagged claims to investigate this month. Recovery, investigator hours, and customer friction pull in different directions: the best recovery-per-hour ratios sit on borderline claims where investigating a legitimate customer costs goodwill. A quarterly recovery target and a hard hours budget couple the picks \u2014 the plan must earn the target inside the capacity \u2014 under per-line concentration caps and four regulator-mandated referrals.",
